<title>UK: Banco Mello sets $100 mln 2-tranche bond.</title>
<headline>Banco Mello sets $100 mln 2-tranche bond.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-06-30</dateline>
<text>
<p>The following two-tranche subordinated bond was announced by lead manager Salomon.  BORROWER   BANCO MELLO (CAYMAN) LTD</p>
<p>GUARANTOR  BANCO MELLO SA</p>
<p>* * * TRANCHE A * * *</p>
<p> AMT    $75 MLN	 BASE	 3MLIBOR   MATURITY   *PERPETUAL</p>
<p> TYPE   FRN	     MARGIN     +150 BP   PAY DATE    30.JUN.97</p>
<p> FULL FEES  75 BP     ISSUE	PAR</p>
<p>NOTES  *CALL ON 30.JUN.02, WHEN COUPON STEPS UP TO 3ML+300 BP</p>
<p>* * * TRANCHE B * * *</p>
<p> AMT    $25 MLN	 COUPON   **8.125     MATURITY    PERPETUAL</p>
<p> TYPE   FRN	     ISSUE	99.575    PAY DATE    30.JUN.97</p>
<p>FULL FEES  75 BP</p>
<p>NOTES  **UNTIL 30.JUN.02, WHEN BECOMES FRN WITH A COUPON OF</p>
<p>	    3ML+300 BP PAYABLE QUARTERLY IF NOT CALLED. CALLABLE</p>
<p>AT</p>
<p>	    PAR AND EVERY INTEREST PAYMENT AFTER 30.JUN.02</p>
<p>* * * COMMON TERMS * * *</p>
<p> MOODY	UNRATED   LISTING     LUX</p>
<p> S&amp;P	  UNRATED   SALE LIMITS US</p>
<p> CRS DEFLT  YES	 GOV LAW     ENGLISH</p>
<p>-- London Newsroom +44 171 542 7658</p>
